barney is a dinosaur from our imagination and when he's tall he's what we call a dinosaur sensation barney's friends are big and small they come from lots of places after school they meet to play and sing with happy faces barney shows us lots of things like how to play pretend a b c's and s and how to be a friend barney comes to play with us whenever we may need him barney can be your friend too if you just make-believe him you might also like